== Ubuzima bwe bwite ==
Uwineza Clarisse ni umubyeyi w'abana babiri ni umunyamakuru akaba n'umuvugabutumwa, mu buzima bwa Clarisse hari ibihe byiza n'bibi, mubihe bye byiza harimo kuba ari umubyeyi, kuba akora akazi akunda, hari n'ibibi  yahuye na byo mu buzima byamukomereye, harimo kurwara Covid-19 inshuro ebyiri, kurwara kanseri ndetse n’igihe yatandukanaga n’uwo bari barashakanye.

Clarisse yashenguwe  no  gutandukana n'umugabo we kuko yumvaga ntacyo atakoze ngo babane neza, mubindi bibi byamubayeho ni ugusanga arwaye kanseri kuko yabimenye nyuma yo gutandukana nuwari umufasha we, bityo bimubera ibizazane, avugako yafashijwe no gusenga ndetse no kwizera Imana.
